summary: This a mod that merged SoS - The Wilds, The Dungeons and Civilizations together. I have also included an MCM mod in the merge. Original files are needed!
descriptionHtml:
This a mod that merged SoS - The Wilds, The Dungeons and Civilizations together. I have also included an MCM mod in the merge. I haven't tested this mod thoroughly, so it is possible a bug could occur. Please let me know if you find any.

Original mod files are needed, except their ESP's!
[b]
Credits go to the original authors of the mods needed by this mod.[/b]
author: Cliffworms and Wormheart and Thane and Mitsarugi and Willy4x4 and LimitSkies
